highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Jaipur. “Kesariya” is the highest at #7.
“Maan Meri Jaan” by King has been on Top Songs Jaipur the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
“Tujhe Kitna Chahne Lage (From "Kabir Singh")” by Arijit Singh and Mithoon is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Jaipur, up 35 spots at #55.
“Amli Anthem” by Raka is the highest new entry on Top Songs Jaipur at #30.
